name: v0.9.2
body: - Should fix some VPN crash issues during running.

name: v0.9.1
body:
- Smooth scrolling text views.
- Update V2Ray assets.
- Highlight zero-download-size requests.

name: v0.9.0
body:
- Update Core.
- Now you can subscribe a complete configuration file from an URL.
- Allow to change sniffing settings for tun2socks.
- Allow to change the inbound tag for tun2socks.
- Now it's your responsibility to provide the correct config for handling DNS requests, see readme for an example.

name: v0.8.0
body:
- Supported Per-App VPN
- Allow quick start/stop the VPN from Quick Settings (requires Android 7.0 or above)
- Allow to disable proxy logging
- Allow to hide DNS logs in proxy log list
- Allow to change the local DNS resolver
